item.title: Summer Somewhere - Black Sunglasses
item.dc:creator: sunglass
item.content:encoded:
The Persol PO3007V Eyeglasses have a simple, yet attractive, appearance. As the oval frame is crafted from premium acetate, these eyeglasses stay strong and tough. The Havana color of the frame gives these glasses a classic touch with a unique retro twist. The Persol signature appears on one of the lenses and on each arm. You can add prescription lenses to these glasses.

Perfect for a casual date or when meeting your friends over the weekend, these retro glasses will go well with any casual outfit in your wardrobe. content: smartbuyglasses
item.excerpt:encoded: Timeless, fashionable, and cool, the Persol PO3007V Eyeglasses just got reinvented! Designed for both men and women, these eyeglasses are perfect for everyday wear. They support customizable lenses and have a Havana-colored, oval frame made from acetate. These Persol eyeglasses can be worn with casual outfits like a floral dress or a graphic tee.

item.title: Nashbar Single-Speed Road Bike
item.dc:creator: Bouba
item.content:encoded:
A cool feature is that this bike includes two handlebars - a drop bar (installed) as well as a bullhorn bar - so you can set the bike up according to your preferred style, yet easily swap it out if desired to change things up. Additionally, caliper brakes deliver all the stopping power you need for safe cycling.
  • FRAME:ALX XC XTrail, 2Thru System, 120mm travel, Post mount, Internal shift cable routing
  • FORK:SR Suntour XCR LOR Air, 120mm travel
  • REAR SHOCK:SR Suntour Raidon-Lo Air, 190x51mm, M8x22mm
  • HEADSET:FSA NO.57B-1, Taper ID: 44mm/56mm
  • CRANKSET:2-piece crank, 40/30/22T chainrings
  • BOTTOM BRACKET:Integrated BB BSA
  • SHIFTERS:Shimano Deore SL-M610, 3x10-speed
  • SEATPOST:Entity Xpert, Alloy, 30.9x350mm
  • LEVERS:Shimano BL-M365 hydraulic disc
  • FRONT DERAILLEUR:Shimano Deore FD-M612-H
  • HANDLEBAR:Entity Xpert, Alloy, 740mm width
  • STEM:Entity Xpert, Alloy, 60mm
  • CASSETTE:Shimano CS-HG50, 10-speed, 11-36T
  • BRAKES:Shimano BR-M365 hydraulic disc, 160mm rotors front/rear
  • WHEELSET:27.5" Araya DM-650 rims, Alloy hubs
  • TIRES:Schwalbe Smart Sam, 27.5"x2.25"
  • PEDALS:VP Component VP-195E, Alloy
  • SADDLE:Entity Assault, Cr-Mo rails
  • CHAIN:KMC X-10
  • GRIPS/TAPE:Entity grips
  • REAR DERAILLEUR:Shimano SLX RD-M7000-10-SGS, Direct mount
item.excerpt:encoded: Simplicity and the joy of riding are what the Nashbar Single-Speed Road Bike is all about. It's perfect for commuting to work, running errands, general fitness riding, or just anytime you feel so inclined to hop on and go for a spin. Its steel frame and fork are as tough as nails and reduce road feedback,
